	   <tr><td colspan=2>There are plenty of places to still get exp, in the old world up through 52, and a few places to get it even up to the mid-50's.&nbsp;&nbsp;And the hole will give you exp up to lvl 60.<br><br>I have a magician and on guild raids, in Kedge or the Hole, a stone is VERY useful.  In kedge, I swim to the safe spot outside Phin's lair, and make sure I CotH a couple healers on my first bar of mana.  I then procede to stone myself, and while the healers are healing I can summon 15 people in a couple min.  CotH = 500 mana (15 x 500 = 7500 mana) Conventionally, it would take at least 30 min to med up all this mana.<br>Yes, everyone could swim there with invis, but, 15 people with invis, and maybe only 2 people know the way, so people get lost, invis drops, they click on something they shouldn't, people die and it turns into a mess.<br><br>-Beltath<br>&nbsp;<br>Beltath of Sol Ro</td></tr>
